## MCP config for Claude Code

Add to `~/.claude/settings.json` to wire MCP:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "parametric-memory": {
      "command": "sh",
      "args": ["-c", "cd /path/to/parametric-memory && set -a && . .env && set +a && npm run mcp:serve"],
      "env": {
        "MMPM_MCP_BASE_URL": "http://127.0.0.1:3000"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

